{"tid":1305890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[九龍灣廢老打人事件] 唔好比人帶風向呀 記住我地初心係乜","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:47:20.000Z","uid":39427,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0cba8696edf98dbec39c3c02add55aed07651b68","tid":1305890,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比人spin去 和理非vs勇武呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當事人唔還手唔代表再有類似事件發生嘅時候都唔應該還手<br />\n兄弟爬山 每人嘅理念可能有啲唔同 但我地嘅目標同終點係一致嘅<br />\n<br />\n當事人相信  &ldquo;Violence will cause violence&rdquo; 我地respect 但唔好話人on9打不還手<br />\n<br />\n下次有兄弟遇到相同嘅事時選擇以武制暴 我地一樣要支持 我地都唔想佢地比人指責同割蓆<br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span> 呀"},{"pid":"9719f50a1de7b90b57a4cf8a20b21c503bf426ca","tid":1305890,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f3b079edff348ad3e4736c210e0febd410c24a09","tid":1305890,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ce045cf8a4a044dbd8a2800e3b4e5d947637c3f","tid":1305890,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd9623f29ec52fc4ac8388ffe9d3a720f4f36162","tid":1305890,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e423a4103c4664d0043bf1412ab2f02a59f91f80","tid":1305890,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"82140af0153976913f1bcea8d731b41f1ceacf45","tid":1305890,"uid":39427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"